
Tripletail
==========

Tripletail is an open-source framework which is for web applications
treat Japanese. It is supposed to run on Linux + Apache + MySQL + Perl.


INSTALLATION
~~~~~~~~~~~~
To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


DEPENDENCIES
~~~~~~~~~~~~
requires:
    Crypt::CBC
    Crypt::Rijndael
    Data::Dumper
    DBI
    Digest::HMAC_SHA1
    File::Path
    IO::Scalar
    MIME::Tools                    5.411
    PadWalker                      1.0
    Test::Exception
    Test::More
    Text::CSV_XS
    Unicode::Japanese


SEE ALSO
~~~~~~~~

For further information, please refer to http://tripletail.jp/


